## 2.2 Knowledge service (Port 8002)

### 2.2.1 Startup lifecycle

On startup:

1. Connect Qdrant.
2. Initialize embedder (`TextEmbedding`, default `BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5`).
3. Ensure collection exists with cosine distance.
4. Load GDPR chunks JSONL.
5. Reindex if collection empty (or forced).

Point IDs are deterministic UUID5 hashes of `chunk_id`.

### 2.2.2 Retrieval API

`POST /search`:

- Input: `query`, `k` (1..20)
