`GET /chunks/{chunk_id}`:

- Scroll-filter by payload field `chunk_id`
- Return full chunk payload

Metrics:

- `retrieval_query_total`
- `retrieval_latency_seconds`
- `retrieval_results_returned_total`
- `chunk_lookup_total`

