## 6. RAG layer details

## 6.1 Retrieval query generation

`_build_retrieval_query(section, topic, mode)` builds context-guided text with mode article hints.

## 6.2 Mode-aware reranking

- privacy_notice mode boosts notice-centric article sets.
- penalizes Article 88 unless employment signals present.
- penalizes Article 30 unless ROPA signals present.

## 6.3 Evidence sufficiency and retry

- retry on weak top score or low keyword overlap.
- sufficiency requires both score strength and obligation-language presence.

## 6.4 Citation gates

- citation must map to retrieved chunk universe.
- article number and paragraph compatibility checks.
- claim/article matrix enforces issue-family legal fit.

